# Asset Management Standards

## Asset Directory Structure
```
assets/
├── css/
│   └── style.scss          # GitHub Pages Jekyll styling entry point
├── images/
│   ├── myob-banner.png    # Main MYOB banner for README
│   └── diagrams/          # Technical diagrams and flowcharts
_sass/
└── myob-styles.scss       # MYOB-specific SCSS variables and styles
```

## Image Asset Management

### Image Naming Conventions
```markdown
# Good naming patterns
myob-banner.png             # Main branding banner
architecture-diagram.png   # Technical diagrams
workflow-flowchart.svg     # Process flows (prefer SVG)
screenshot-feature-x.png   # Feature screenshots
```

### Image Reference Standards
```markdown
# Correct image references from markdown files
![MYOB Banner](assets/images/myob-banner.png)

# For pages in subdirectories, use relative paths
![Architecture Diagram](../../assets/images/diagrams/architecture-diagram.png)
```

### Image Requirements
- **Format**: PNG for screenshots, SVG for diagrams when possible
- **Size**: Optimize for web (< 500KB for most images)
- **Alt Text**: Always include descriptive alt text
- **MYOB Branding**: Use official MYOB colors and styling

