## File Size and Performance

### Size Limits
- **Images**: < 500KB for regular images, < 1MB for detailed diagrams
- **CSS**: Keep compiled CSS < 100KB
- **Total Assets**: Monitor total asset size impact on page load

### Performance Optimization
```markdown
# Use appropriate image formats
- PNG: Screenshots, images with text
- JPEG: Photographs, complex images
- SVG: Icons, simple diagrams, logos
- WebP: Modern browsers, when file size is critical
```

### Loading Optimization
```html
<!-- Use lazy loading for images below the fold -->
<img src="assets/images/diagram.png" alt="Diagram" loading="lazy">

<!-- Preload critical images -->
<link rel="preload" as="image" href="assets/images/myob-banner.png">
```